title: Nepali Kitchen and Coffee House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Take-out, Nepalese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu doesn't state which dishes are vegan, but the thali, momo, and veg curry are supposed to be vegan suitable. Other vegetarians dishes could be made vegan upon request. Shares the same space with Collage, and you could order from either menu.
